snippet.title: Virtua Fighter 5 R (2008) Newcomers Playthrough (60 FPS) SEGA Lindbergh (ARCADE) iPlaySEGA
snippet.description:
Welcome to iPLAY SEGA!! Episode 28!
This is my very first SEGA Lindbergh Arcade Hardware Video at 60 FPS!
Let's start with my favorite 3D fighting game series, Virtua Fighter!
This is the arcade exclusive '5 R' version from 2008.

You will see a full playthrough of both 'newcomers' (Jean Kujo & the from VF3 returning Taka Arashi)

Played on real Arcade Hardware and captured at 60 FPS!
BTW: HEY SEGA!! Where is our VF6...?

Find me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/iPlaySEGA
Find me on Facebook: https://facebook.com/iPlaySEGA
Find me on Instagram: https://instagram.com/iPlaySEGAofficial

Thanks for watching!

Video: ©iPlaySEGA
